reviewText: This is one of the sexiest DVDs I've ever seen. Tiffany Brooks has the sexiest scenes to me, and Lisa A. Daniels is not far behind her. Amy Reid, Alexa Rae and Rachel Elizabeth are also noteworthy. There are some other girls, but these five are enough for me. Jelena Jensen and Crissy Moran just aren't my cup of tea, and Nissa isn't memorable in my book. Oh well, 2 fine girls with great scenes and 3 sexy more girls with good scenes are enough to make this DVD worth buying. 8 is a big cast for such movies, so if I don't like 3 so well, it's no big deal. Many such movies only have 4 or 5 girls, so with 8 of them, this DVD should please anyone.
